    "form_instructions_text": "Instructions:\nDeadlines - Each form is due to this office by March 3 COB. Individual Form Required - each request by each requesting entity requires an individual form, so if you have multiple requests, please fill out a separate form for each. This includes if you have a funding request and a language request for the same issue, that is two separate requests. Non-Defense Form Only - this form is only for Non-Defense Programmatic requests. For all Programmatic Defense requests, please use the separate form linked here: https://forms.cloud.microsoft/g/ZsuFz3V4SL Please reach out to Rep. Cline's office if you are seeking guidance on Community Project Funding requests.\n\nImportant - there are 31 questions. If less than that, answer the last question shown and the rest will appear.",
